donor_name: UNDP AS ADMINISTRATIVE AGENT FOR A JOINT PROGRAMME PASS THROUGH ARRANGEMENT
outputs.output_descr: A gender responsive national human rights action plan developed in a participatory manner and implemented

project_descr: The project will strengthen the capacity of key State and Non-State Actors (government departments, CSOs, NGOs and CBOs) in Human Rights and will enhance their engagement with the state party reporting and Universal Periodic Review (UPR) process.
